{"tid":869513,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【淡友末日】財金高官齊開腔撑A股　分析料救市措施續來","createTime":"2018-10-20T11:39:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-21T15:13:18.000Z","uid":66271,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"de54bbc76cd9bcc48eeab44717b217114eb49d4f","tid":869513,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T11:39:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2185000/2189943/20AB001_S_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2185000%2F2189943%2F20AB001_S_1024.jpg&h=436d0b13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地第三季增速放緩至6.5%，低過預期，引發市場恐慌，副總理劉鶴和「一行兩會」掌門人昨齊齊發聲撑股市和經濟。分析指，劉鶴表態維穩代表最高層，意味維穩政策和救市措施將陸續出台。<br />\n<br />\n劉鶴接受中央媒體訪問稱，股市近期出現明顯波動和下滑是諸多因素造成，並引用國際投資機構看法稱，中國股市泡沫已大大縮小，估值處於歷史低位，而股市的調整和供需的調節正為長期健康發展創造良好投資機會。<br />\n<br />\n劉鶴：貿戰影響心理大於實際<br />\n<br />\n他強調，政府高度重視股市的健康穩定發展，中國政府將深化改革開放，沒有理由不對中國經濟發展廣闊前景充滿信心。他又指，中美貿易摩擦對市場的心理影響大於實際影響，目前雙方正在接觸。<br />\n<br />\n同時，一行兩會掌門人，即人民銀行行長易綱、中國銀保監主席郭樹清和中證監主席劉士余，昨日開市前齊發聲支持股市，以穩定市場信心。<br />\n<br />\n易綱表示，近期內地股市波動，主要受情緒影響，又稱內地股市估值已處歷史低位。郭樹清則稱，允許保險資金設立專項產品，參與化解上市公司股票質押流動性風險。劉士余指，近期推進6大措施穩定和提振市場信心。<br />\n<br />\n淡友係時候要悔改 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2feb32202f019920d918076b2b8dfa97476b6759","tid":869513,"uid":1425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T11:40:25.000Z","msg":"molamola<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07fb52fc3c5f3811444ad0df8e7d4785c523477a","tid":869513,"uid":66271,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"2feb32202f019920d918076b2b8dfa97476b6759","tid":869513,"uid":1425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T11:40:25.000Z","msg":"molamola<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T11:43:05.000Z","msg":"國家要救市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3397d3730ead2a071392ab5636e8a4619d030e9","tid":869513,"uid":41116,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T11:43:06.000Z","msg":"支那垃圾市要每幾多年救一次？<br />\nA 一年<br />\nB 兩年<br />\nC 三年"},{"pid":"b1826686b81c72c9b6ce2dd8eecbef046483d150","tid":869513,"uid":15009,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"d3397d3730ead2a071392ab5636e8a4619d030e9","tid":869513,"uid":41116,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T11:43:06.000Z","msg":"支那垃圾市要每幾多年救一次？<br />\nA 一年<br />\nB 兩年<br />\nC 三年"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T11:43:50.000Z","msg":"D每日"},{"pid":"7dd403dea8dc1849a54666e33adb7ee0e972047f","tid":869513,"uid":97518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T11:45:36.000Z","msg":"救得一日得一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd14e063de7aaf0535c1573805e4c264640a3343","tid":869513,"uid":152742,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1826686b81c72c9b6ce2dd8eecbef046483d150","tid":869513,"uid":15009,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"d3397d3730ead2a071392ab5636e8a4619d030e9","tid":869513,"uid":41116,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T11:43:06.000Z","msg":"支那垃圾市要每幾多年救一次？<br />\nA 一年<br />\nB 兩年<br />\nC 三年"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T11:43:50.000Z","msg":"D每日"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T11:45:39.000Z","msg":"E 逢星期五"},{"pid":"461e988527df